1. *Priču* sam čuo od starijeg čoveka. (I heard the story from an older man.)
2. Ona je znala da *priča* o tome. (She knew how to talk about it.)
3. On je često *pričao* o svojim problemima. (He often talked about his problems.)
4. Ona je *pričala* na jeziku koga nisam razumeo. (She was speaking in a language I couldn't understand.)
5. *Pričam* o tome već godinama. (I've been talking about it for years.)